INSERT INTO oauth_handoffs (
                provider,
                state,
                return_to,
                app_challenge,
                expires_at,
                server_owned,
                server_verifier
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
            RETURNING
                id              AS "id!",
                provider        AS "provider!",
                state           AS "state!",
                return_to       AS "return_to!",
                app_challenge   AS "app_challenge!",
                app_code_hash   AS "app_code_hash?",
                status          AS "status!",
                error_code      AS "error_code?",
                expires_at      AS "expires_at!",
                authorized_at   AS "authorized_at?",
                redeemed_at     AS "redeemed_at?",
                user_id         AS "user_id?",
                session_id      AS "session_id?",
                server_owned    AS "server_owned!",
                server_verifier AS "server_verifier?",
                created_at      AS "created_at!",
                updated_at      AS "updated_at!"
